org.afplib.afplib

Interface BDD

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SF
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BDDImpl

    public interface BDD
extends SF
    A representation of the model object 'BDD'.

    The following features are supported:

    • UBASE
    • Reserved
    • XUPUB
    • YUPUB
    • XEXTENT
    • YEXTENT
    • Reserved2
    • TYPE
    • MOD
    • LID
    • COLOR
    • MODULEWIDTH
    • ELEMENTHEIGHT
    • MULT
    • WENE
    • Triplets

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getBDD()
